                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "is the natural logarithm. This means that the expected gap between two consecutive "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "n"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "-bit primes is "
